## ---------------------------------------------
## SECRETS — never commit real credentials
## Keep real DB passwords / API keys in
## .NET user-secrets (dev) and environment
## variables (production), NOT in these files.
## appsettings.json is COMMITTED — use placeholders only.
## ---------------------------------------------
appsettings.*.Local.json
secrets.json
*.pfx
*.key
.env
.env.*

## OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
